{"tid":1317061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要勇武？勇武有乜用？","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:19:24.000Z","uid":203973,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc16011ffdd8af492aeec5ff4c5e48e29d654f3","tid":1317061,"uid":203973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:21:22.000Z","msg":"見到愈嚟愈多人勇武<span style=\"color: pink;\">覺醒</span><br />\n又係時候審視下之後條路點行<br />\n<br />\n我相信冇把握嘅仗冇人想打<br />\n我相信其實<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">好多人都想勇武</span><br />\n但大家都唔知條勇武抗爭路線係點行......<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>打贏咗前線狗之後點？繼續推進去邊？係咪會迫到班狗出水砲/開槍，前線個個頭破血流之後點？始終裝備差距太大。大部分人民心態未準備好有可能死。進一步諗，真係全民起義，打贏班黑警，咁就代表推翻到政權？中共係咪會出老解鎮壓？國際社會到底會唔會趁機出軍保香港？(暫時嚟睇機會好微)</em></span><br />\n<br />\n無論勇武/和理非，我覺得最重要嘅作用力有二:<br />\n<br />\n一，喚醒更多香港人，達至真正<span style=\"color: red;\">全民起義</span><br />\n<br />\n二，吸引更多<span style=\"color: purple;\">國際關注</span>，增加必要時以任何方式幫助香港人嘅機會，包括各種經濟制裁，用國際威脅力談判，接收政治難民，甚至出兵<br />\n<br />\n香港係冇自己軍隊，黑警亦冇可能變節，只有靠自己人醒覺+國際幫助，香港先有機會得救！<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">勇武抗爭就係一切嘅導火線</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復行動</span>一定要持續，要令國際社會清楚知道，更要大大聲話俾中共同蝗知道:<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港係屬於香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後切記，<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Be Water</span></span>，頭破血流嘅唔應該係義士，打暴徒可以，但請不要戀戰，衝突背後，人面獸心嘅港共高層仍然食緊花生，莫忘初衷！"},{"pid":"b6e72e2c1adbb4d177949b8001c5e67e9b838fe1","tid":1317061,"uid":118787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"共勉之"},{"pid":"6ab561193ddca8f1fa9421471bb240c79fa89c7d","tid":1317061,"uid":196114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d89838520258b98663c0a0bf6c36be9c85c17bb1","tid":1317061,"uid":203973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:22:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8e0d041fb7c171fb6ee8b13ce64922e96a0f842a","tid":1317061,"uid":119478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"香港人應該好適合做archer"},{"pid":"e8cef9dff7911e9acba61cef8f5a0085a5c95748","tid":1317061,"uid":60398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日又要佔領輿論，港台商台火力全開</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n0800-1000 香港電台第一台<br />\n千禧年代 / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n1700-1800 香港電台第一台<br />\n自由風自由Phone / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n0630-0700, 0715-1000 雷霆881 (陳志雲版)<br />\n0800-1000 叱咤903 (潘小濤版)<br />\n在晴朗的一天出發 / Phone in 電話: 1872881 (陳) / 1872903 (潘)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係入去商場食飯架<br />\n點解警察要用警棍打我呀？<br />\n<br />\n大家自己諗好大家嘅身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">同場加映</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JiOnfAc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiOnfAc.png&h=39ea108e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77b15611a5ebda23aa7e815b038a92ec94516b6d","tid":1317061,"uid":203973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ab0884b612d3e00da05073830ee79ac8e584f9c1","tid":1317061,"uid":203973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91e024bfb38962627ef10a981b2f9c380143a14e","tid":1317061,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"今之真係俾班黑警迫入絕警"},{"pid":"8554a673e417c0cb724eda5b49197b32df1caf2d","tid":1317061,"uid":203973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"香港人要醒啦！"},{"pid":"90b8e73db6bc7